{
  "texts": [
    "By contrasting the two parameters, GFLOPs and FPS, with those of other models using the NEU-DET and GC10-DET datasets, we were able to increase the model's detection accuracy.",
    "The GFLOPs have gone up from Baseline, although they are still lower than in other models.",
    "The model's frame rate per second has dropped.",
    "For more information, see Tables 2 and 3.",
    "Ablation experiments were conducted to evaluate the impacts of MSF and CRA block and investigate the performance of the YOLOv5s model on the NEU-DET and GC10-DET datasets."
  ]
}